{"tid":1972302,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"印度封城，恆河水質大幅改善：可達直接飲用水標準！","createTime":"2020-04-14T12:21:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-24T16:31:05.000Z","uid":109923,"like":11,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"05a186a0eab6bbb44837eb01faf252196ceab118","tid":1972302,"uid":109923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T12:21:54.000Z","msg":"由於nmsl武漢病毒疫情蔓延，全球多個國家都在封閉城市，禁止人員流動。對人類來說這是個麻煩，對大自然來說，少了人類活動可能是好事，印度的恆河水質就變好了，甚至達到了直飲水標準。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n據環球援引印度媒體報道，自從3月份以來，印度因新冠肺炎疫情實施全國封鎖，恆河兩岸工廠全部停工，恆河水質得到大幅改善，現在河水已經適合飲用了，印度中央污染控制委員會（CPCB）表示：「大部分河段的水源已經達到直接飲用標準。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n在此之前，2019年5月，印度中央污染控制委員會（CPCB）曾表示，來自聖河恆河的水絕對不適合「直接飲用」。<br />\n<br />\n2019年10月，北方邦污染管理局（UPPCB）稱恆河水甚至不適合洗澡。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n恆河長達2510公里，流域面積佔到印度全境1/3，同時也是印度的聖河，在恆河中沐浴是印度人的一種習俗，認為此舉能夠淨化心靈。<br />\n<br />\n不過恆河在2007年被評為世界五條污染最嚴重的河流之一。在瓦拉納西所測得的水中糞生大腸桿菌群超過印度政府所訂標準值100倍以上。污染不僅對人類造成危害，也對140種魚類、90種兩生類及瀕危的恆河豚造成威脅。"},{"pid":"6bda70d95daf28aa17ac7bcfce616b4478ffe415","tid":1972302,"uid":125168,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T12:22:50.000Z","msg":"達到直接飲用標準<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />吹到咁大"},{"pid":"e675b69ff980e631485e5caf1fda7d1bab83ff94","tid":1972302,"uid":55458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T12:24:16.000Z","msg":"狗飲"},{"pid":"81a8d07876d8f6a2ddda265a6ed024a8a703d45e","tid":1972302,"uid":30678,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"quote":{"pid":"6bda70d95daf28aa17ac7bcfce616b4478ffe415","tid":1972302,"uid":125168,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T12:22:50.000Z","msg":"達到直接飲用標準<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />吹到咁大"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T12:24:27.000Z","msg":"達到印度人飲用標準<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d4c9ee3f98c6e2758702a8b6d70da7a25da59bf","tid":1972302,"uid":39470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6bda70d95daf28aa17ac7bcfce616b4478ffe415","tid":1972302,"uid":125168,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T12:22:50.000Z","msg":"達到直接飲用標準<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />吹到咁大"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T12:25:24.000Z","msg":"飲唔痾佢咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de357f260e90153cca6d28761a5f69f92ee15e65","tid":1972302,"uid":3063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T12:26:45.000Z","msg":"飲完屙爛屎<br />\n+<br />\n寄生蟲"},{"pid":"5a99f80f8555fdb8b94f912155d83ce1b669107b","tid":1972302,"uid":70888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T12:34:12.000Z","msg":"屎水都飲得架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acd1967b0280a3597968ac0bd9510a77fef0bd8b","tid":1972302,"uid":89861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T12:34:41.000Z","msg":"印度佬不嬲直接飲"},{"pid":"fdafbbb993daed0146814443bf7967757331c85d","tid":1972302,"uid":2795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T12:49:27.000Z","msg":"熔岩都飲得架"},{"pid":"16ce06bb859eee238dc70e558ffdc9d398a316f3","tid":1972302,"uid":6752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T12:50:46.000Z","msg":"印度標準<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46001f22ffbd3d29f4fc813aedc01df33163527d","tid":1972302,"uid":103050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T12:53:00.000Z","msg":"環球援引印度媒體<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bde1a27f4a75ac3826d361a69866956a014f7d7","tid":1972302,"uid":137157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T12:54:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/watch?v